妹<br />\nRobin Fong/水警/表弟 ......<br />\n<br />\n(我們邀請警員親屬參與此次聯署，請填上 您的名字/家人工作部門/與家人關係)<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA-%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E8%A6%AA%E5%B1%AC%E8%87%B4%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E9%95%B7%E5%AE%98%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E4%BF%A1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E5%2595%258F%25E9%25A1%258C%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%25B1%25BA-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E8%2587%25B4%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A5%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E4%25BF%25A1%2F&d=5riwYeXkLlljSywqzybc4s%2BSO5qySt9BI5W58Aqq%2Fug%3D&h=0b909b8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E5%2595%258F%25E9%25A1%258C%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%25B1%25BA-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E8%2587%25B4%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A5%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E4%25BF%25A1%2F&h=81ed49b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA-%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E8%A6%AA%E5%B1%AC%E8%87%B4%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E9%95%B7%E5%AE%98%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E4%BF%A1/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />D名 老豆又揾仔啦"},{"pid":"21f2ca53792b9279c2c18080b79010c8a91bf913","tid":1335537,"uid":282